replies.body:
Updating your system drivers as *Dadron3* mentioned is a good first step for sure. Typically FPS issues are caused by malfunctioning display drivers or windows power settings. If you continue to see this issue after updating your system drivers, I recommend working through the steps outlined in our [FPS troubleshooting guide.
](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752684-Low-Frame-Rate-FPS-Troubleshooting)

Let me know if those steps caused any change.
